metadata.name: The Universe Within
metadata.description:
'The Universe Within' is the first piece in the Psycatdelic Feline Dreams collection, which is an NFT open edition collection that features a series of digital artworks that showcase surreal and mind-bending dreamlike images in different claim drops. These one-of-a-kind pieces are designed to evoke a sense of wonder and mystery in the viewer. Each drop will mint the same NFT, and there will be multiple drops to the collection.


Imaginary Cat is passionate about cats and psychedelic art. The artworks are created using a combination of Ai and digital painting, resulting in stunning and vibrant visuals.This open edition collection gives me a gateway to share my art outside of the main collections I am working on.


With its vibrant and surreal imagery, Psycatdelic Feline Dreams is sure to appeal to cat lovers, art collectors, and anyone who appreciates the beauty and creativity of digital art.
